BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:tIY7RIVigb9Fmhctuzqpn
SUMMARY:IMPROV 100 SUNDAYS 3:30 pm- Intro to Improv: Say Yes!\\\, SPRING'26
DTSTAMP:20260322T034736Z
DTSTART:20260322T153000Z
DESCRIPTION:Discover Unexpected Productions’ philosophy of improvisation\\\
	, developed over our 43 years of improvising in Seattle! \\nYou’ll learn h
	ow to actively listen\\\, to use your own life to create collaborative sto
	ries\\\, and you’ll work on the fundamental principles of improvisation: w
	hat it means to say\\\, “Yes\\\, And”\\\, how to tell stories that include
	 everyone in the room\\\, how to stop worrying about failing\\\, and the g
	ames and concepts behind what we do on stages around the world! \\nUnder t
	he guidance of one of our best Seattle improv teachers\\\, you will learn 
	to:· \\n\\nBe a Better Listener\\nConquer Fears\\nSpark Creativity\\nMeet 
	New People & Make New Friends\\nBecome a Better Problem Solver\\nGain Conf
	idence·\\nFail With Grace (and Maybe Even Enjoy It)\\nSay Yes More in Your
	 Life\\nGet Out of Your Comfort Zone\\nBecome a Better Public Speaker\\nDi
	scover More About Yourself\\n…and have a blast doing it!\\n\\nTime and Dat
	es: Sundays for eight (8) weeks\\\, from March 22 to May 27\\\, 3:30pm to 
	6:00pm (No class on April 5th) \\nNOTE: Attendance at the first session of
	 your course is mandatory as it sets the agenda for the entire quarter. If
	 you think you will have to miss the first class\\\, please consider regis
	tering for the next quarter. \\nNo Prerequisites. All students begin at th
	is level\\\, even those with existing improv experience. It’s a prerequisi
	te to the other levels. \\nLocation: 5700 6th Ave St\\\, Suite 109\\\, Umb
	rella Room\\\, Seattle\\\, WA 98108 (In Georgetown\\\, south of downtown\\
	\, with plenty of parking.) \\nMaximum Students: 16 \\nCost: Ticket price 
	$295.00 \\nAge: 18 and above \\n**Cancellation policy: If you must cancel 
	before the first class\\\, we can only offer credit towards the same level
	 class next quarter. We are unable to offer refunds. If you cancel after t
	he first class we cannot offer credit towards a future class. Again\\\, we
	 are unable to offer refunds.\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/eve
	nt/improv-100-sundays-330-pm-intro-to-improv-say-yes-spring26/\n\nFrom Une
	xpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/improv-100-sundays-330-pm-i
	ntro-to-improv-say-yes-spring26/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions Improv School ISSAQUAH/EASTSIDE\\\, 1315 NW
	 Mall Street\\\, Suite 4\\\, Issaquah\\\, WA\\\, 98108\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:WjDMMXG9c_bZnnwWTIqu6
SUMMARY:Show Your Game: An Improvised Game Show
DTSTAMP:20260322T034736Z
DTSTART:20260322T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Ever wonder what secret skills your neighbors are hiding? That 
	quiet person next to you on the bus might be a brain surgeon\\\, a barbecu
	e champion\\\, or the only parent in town who can get their toddler to nap
	 on time. Show Your Game is here to celebrate those everyday experts and u
	nexpected talents! \\nEach night\\\, a hilarious mix of improvisers and br
	ave audience members go head-to-head\\\, diving deep into the worlds of tw
	o surprising experts. They’ll tackle quirky questions and wild challenges\
	\\, each crafted by the experts themselves to test just how much our conte
	stants really know. \\nLove the clever chaos of QI\\\, the unpredictable t
	wists of Game Changer\\\, or the absurd fun of Taskmaster? Then this is yo
	ur kind of show. \\nSo\\\, when it’s your turn to step into someone else’s
	 world… are you ready to Show Your Game?\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproducti
	ons.org/event/show-your-game-an-improvised-game-show-3/2026-03-22/\n\nFrom
	 Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/show-your-game-an-improvise
	d-game-show-3/2026-03-22/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
